{
  "script_id": "bell-numbers",
  "voice": "zh-CN-XiaoxiaoNeural",
  "voice_key": "xiaoxiao",
  "files": [
    {
      "script_id": "bell-numbers",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-1",
      "filename": "intro-intro-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/bell-numbers/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.86,
      "size": 29808,
      "text": "假设你有三位朋友，要把他们分成几个小组一起吃饭。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "bell-numbers",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-2",
      "filename": "intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/bell-numbers/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.75,
      "size": 27936,
      "text": "可以三人一桌，可以两人加一人，也可以各坐各的。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "bell-numbers",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-3",
      "filename": "intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/bell-numbers/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.3,
      "size": 20736,
      "text": "数一数，三个人一共有五种分法。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "bell-numbers",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-4",
      "filename": "intro-intro-4.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/bell-numbers/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-4.mp3",
      "duration": 1.61,
      "size": 25776,
      "text": "这个「总共有多少种分法」的数字，就叫贝尔数。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "bell-numbers",
      "section_id": "define",
      "line_id": "def-1",
      "filename": "define-def-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/bell-numbers/xiaoxiao/define-def-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.66,
      "size": 42624,
      "text": "贝尔数 B(n)，就是把 n 个元素的集合划分成若干非空子集的所有方式总数。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "bell-numbers",
      "section_id": "define",
      "line_id": "def-2",
      "filename": "define-def-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/bell-numbers/xiaoxiao/define-def-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.94,
      "size": 47088,
      "text": "B(0) 和 B(1) 都是 1，B(2) 是 2，B(3) 是 5，B(4) 一下跳到 15。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "bell-numbers",
      "section_id": "define",
      "line_id": "def-3",
      "filename": "define-def-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/bell-numbers/xiaoxiao/define-def-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.46,
      "size": 23328,
      "text": "元素每多一个，分法都会爆炸式增长。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "bell-numbers",
      "section_id": "triangle",
      "line_id": "tri-1",
      "filename": "triangle-tri-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/bell-numbers/xiaoxiao/triangle-tri-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.75,
      "size": 28080,
      "text": "有个漂亮的办法能一口气算出它们，叫贝尔三角。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "bell-numbers",
      "section_id": "triangle",
      "line_id": "tri-2",
      "filename": "triangle-tri-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/bell-numbers/xiaoxiao/triangle-tri-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.49,
      "size": 23904,
      "text": "每一行的开头，抄下上一行的末尾那个数。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "bell-numbers",
      "section_id": "triangle",
      "line_id": "tri-3",
      "filename": "triangle-tri-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/bell-numbers/xiaoxiao/triangle-tri-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.74,
      "size": 27792,
      "text": "其余每个数，等于它左边的数加上左上方的数。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "bell-numbers",
      "section_id": "triangle",
      "line_id": "tri-4",
      "filename": "triangle-tri-4.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/bell-numbers/xiaoxiao/triangle-tri-4.mp3",
      "duration": 1.67,
      "size": 26640,
      "text": "于是每一行的末尾，正好就是下一个贝尔数。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "bell-numbers",
      "section_id": "stirling",
      "line_id": "stir-1",
      "filename": "stirling-stir-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/bell-numbers/xiaoxiao/stirling-stir-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.21,
      "size": 35280,
      "text": "如果规定恰好分成 k 个子集，方式数就是第二类斯特林数。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "bell-numbers",
      "section_id": "stirling",
      "line_id": "stir-2",
      "filename": "stirling-stir-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/bell-numbers/xiaoxiao/stirling-stir-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.08,
      "size": 33264,
      "text": "把 k 从 1 加到 n 的所有斯特林数相加，得到的正是贝尔数。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "bell-numbers",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-1",
      "filename": "interaction-int-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/bell-numbers/xiaoxiao/interaction-int-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.65,
      "size": 26352,
      "text": "调整行数，看贝尔三角如何一行行生长。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "bell-numbers",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-2",
      "filename": "interaction-int-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/bell-numbers/xiaoxiao/interaction-int-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.99,
      "size": 31824,
      "text": "盯住每行末尾的高亮数字，那串数就是贝尔数序列。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "bell-numbers",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-1",
      "filename": "summary-sum-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/bell-numbers/xiaoxiao/summary-sum-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.56,
      "size": 24912,
      "text": "贝尔数数清了一个集合所有可能的划分方式。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "bell-numbers",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-2",
      "filename": "summary-sum-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/bell-numbers/xiaoxiao/summary-sum-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.73,
      "size": 27648,
      "text": "贝尔三角用简单的加法，就把它们层层生成出来。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "bell-numbers",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-3",
      "filename": "summary-sum-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/bell-numbers/xiaoxiao/summary-sum-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.68,
      "size": 26928,
      "text": "简单的规则藏着惊人的增长，我们下次再见！"
    }
  ],
  "total_duration": 33.129999999999995,
